### ============================================================================
### ERP TEMPLARIOS - SPRINT 4: AUTOMATION TESTS
### Pruebas de automatización de estados y cálculos automáticos
### Archivo para VS Code REST Client
### ============================================================================

### Variables de entorno
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### ============================================================================
### AUTENTICACIÓN (Login para obtener token)
### ============================================================================

### Login como admin
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@templarios.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Guardar token de acceso
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### SETUP: OBTENER DATOS EXISTENTES
### ============================================================================

### Obtener BLs disponibles
# @name getBLs
GET {{baseUrl}}/bl?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

@blId = {{getBLs.response.body.data.bls[0].id}}

### Obtener camiones disponibles
# @name getTrucks
GET {{baseUrl}}/fleet/trucks?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

@truckId = {{getTrucks.response.body.data.trucks[0].id}}

### Obtener conductores disponibles
# @name getDrivers
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

@driverId = {{getDrivers.response.body.data.drivers[0].id}}

### Obtener remolques disponibles
# @name getTrailers
GET {{baseUrl}}/fleet/trailers?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

@trailerId = {{getTrailers.response.body.data.trailers[0].id}}

### Obtener clientes
# @name getClients
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

@clientId = {{getClients.response.body.data.clients[0].id}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 1: VERIFICACIÓN DE RECURSOS DISPONIBLES
### ============================================================================

### Obtener recursos disponibles (camiones, conductores, remolques)
# @name getAvailableResources
GET {{baseUrl}}/trips/available
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 2: CREAR VIAJE - VALIDACIÓN DE RECURSOS
### ============================================================================

### Crear nuevo viaje
# @name createTrip
POST {{baseUrl}}/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "micDta": "MIC-AUTO-TEST-001",
  "departureDate": "2024-06-20T06:00:00Z",
  "billOfLadingId": "{{blId}}",
  "truckId": "{{truckId}}",
  "driverId": "{{driverId}}",
  "trailerId": "{{trailerId}}",
  "weight": 30.5,
  "ratePerTon": 150.00,
  "notes": "Viaje de prueba para automatización"
}

@tripId = {{createTrip.response.body.data.id}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 3: VERIFICAR ESTADO INICIAL DEL CAMIÓN Y CONDUCTOR
### ============================================================================

### Verificar estado del camión (debe seguir SCHEDULED porque el viaje está SCHEDULED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/fleet/trucks/{{truckId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Verificar disponibilidad del conductor (debe seguir disponible)
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/{{driverId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 4: TRANSICIÓN SCHEDULED → IN_TRANSIT (Verificar automatización)
### ============================================================================

### Cambiar estado del viaje a IN_TRANSIT
# @name startTrip
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/trips/{{tripId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "IN_TRANSIT"
}

### Verificar que el camión ahora está IN_TRANSIT
# @name checkTruckInTransit
GET {{baseUrl}}/fleet/trucks/{{truckId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Verificar que el conductor ahora NO está disponible
# @name checkDriverUnavailable
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/{{driverId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 5: TRANSICIÓN IN_TRANSIT → AT_BORDER (Auto-creación de Border Crossing)
### ============================================================================

### Cambiar estado del viaje a AT_BORDER
# @name tripToBorder
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/trips/{{tripId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "AT_BORDER"
}

### Verificar que el camión ahora está AT_BORDER
GET {{baseUrl}}/fleet/trucks/{{truckId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 6: VERIFICAR AUTO-CREACIÓN DE BORDER CROSSING
### ============================================================================

### Obtener cruces de frontera del viaje (debe existir uno creado automáticamente)
# @name getBorderCrossingsByTrip
GET {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings/trip/{{tripId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

@borderCrossingId = {{getBorderCrossingsByTrip.response.body.data[0].id}}

### Obtener fronteras activas
GET {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings/active
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener todos los cruces de frontera con paginación
GET {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings?page=1&limit=10&status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener nombres de fronteras disponibles
GET {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings/names
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 7: GESTIÓN DE CANALES EN FRONTERA
### ============================================================================

### Cambiar canal a YELLOW
POST {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings/{{borderCrossingId}}/channel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "channel": "YELLOW",
  "reason": "Revisión documental requerida",
  "notes": "Documentos en revisión",
  "responsible": "Oficial Aduanero Pérez"
}

### Obtener historial de canales
GET {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings/{{borderCrossingId}}/history
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Cambiar canal a GREEN
POST {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings/{{borderCrossingId}}/channel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "channel": "GREEN",
  "reason": "Documentación en orden"
}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 8: REGISTRAR SALIDA DE FRONTERA (Auto-cambio a IN_TRANSIT)
### ============================================================================

### Registrar salida de frontera
# @name registerExit
POST {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings/{{borderCrossingId}}/exit
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Verificar que el camión volvió a IN_TRANSIT
GET {{baseUrl}}/fleet/trucks/{{truckId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Verificar que el viaje volvió a IN_TRANSIT
GET {{baseUrl}}/trips/{{tripId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 9: CREAR BORDER CROSSING MANUAL
### ============================================================================

### Primero poner el viaje en AT_BORDER de nuevo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/trips/{{tripId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "AT_BORDER"
}

### Crear un nuevo cruce de frontera manualmente
# @name createBorderCrossing
POST {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tripId": "{{tripId}}",
  "borderName": "Aduana Tambo Quemado",
  "arrivedAt": "2024-06-20T15:30:00Z"
}

@manualBorderCrossingId = {{createBorderCrossing.response.body.data.id}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 10: TRANSICIÓN A DELIVERED (Liberación de recursos)
### ============================================================================

### Registrar salida del cruce manual
POST {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings/{{manualBorderCrossingId}}/exit
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Cambiar estado del viaje a DELIVERED
# @name deliverTrip
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/trips/{{tripId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "DELIVERED"
}

### Verificar que el camión volvió a estar disponible (SCHEDULED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/fleet/trucks/{{truckId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Verificar que el conductor volvió a estar disponible
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/{{driverId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 11: CÁLCULO AUTOMÁTICO DE LIQUIDACIÓN
### ============================================================================

### Obtener cálculo automático de liquidación desde el viaje
# @name calculateSettlement
GET {{baseUrl}}/settlements/calculate/{{tripId}}?exchangeRate=6.93
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Crear liquidación con valores calculados
# @name createSettlement
POST {{baseUrl}}/settlements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tripId": "{{tripId}}",
  "freightUsd": 4575.00,
  "freightBob": 31704.75,
  "exchangeRate": 6.93,
  "pricePerTon": 150.00,
  "taxIt3Percent": 951.14,
  "retention7Percent": 2219.33,
  "externalCommission": 200.00,
  "advance": 5000.00,
  "notes": "Liquidación con cálculos automáticos"
}

@settlementId = {{createSettlement.response.body.data.id}}

### Obtener estadísticas de liquidaciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/settlements/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 12: CÁLCULO AUTOMÁTICO DE FACTURA
### ============================================================================

### Calcular factura desde múltiples viajes
# @name calculateInvoice
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices/calculate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tripIds": ["{{tripId}}"],
  "exchangeRate": 6.93
}

### Crear factura
# @name createInvoice
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "invoiceNumber": "INV-AUTO-TEST-001",
  "clientId": "{{clientId}}",
  "invoiceDate": "2024-06-20",
  "totalAmount": 31704.75,
  "amountUsd": 4575.00,
  "exchangeRate": 6.93,
  "tripIds": ["{{tripId}}"],
  "notes": "Factura generada con cálculos automáticos"
}

@invoiceId = {{createInvoice.response.body.data.id}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 13: FLUJO DE APROBACIÓN
### ============================================================================

### Aprobar liquidación
POST {{baseUrl}}/settlements/{{settlementId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Marcar liquidación como pagada
POST {{baseUrl}}/settlements/{{settlementId}}/pay
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Emitir factura
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Marcar factura como pagada
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/pay
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 14: VERIFICACIÓN DE VALIDACIONES
### ============================================================================

### Intentar crear liquidación para un viaje no entregado (debe fallar)
# @name createTrip2
POST {{baseUrl}}/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "micDta": "MIC-AUTO-TEST-002",
  "departureDate": "2024-06-21T06:00:00Z",
  "billOfLadingId": "{{blId}}",
  "truckId": "{{truckId}}",
  "driverId": "{{driverId}}",
  "weight": 25.0,
  "ratePerTon": 150.00
}

@tripId2 = {{createTrip2.response.body.data.id}}

### Intentar crear liquidación (debe fallar - viaje no entregado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/settlements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tripId": "{{tripId2}}",
  "freightUsd": 3750.00,
  "freightBob": 25987.50,
  "exchangeRate": 6.93,
  "pricePerTon": 150.00,
  "taxIt3Percent": 779.63,
  "retention7Percent": 1819.13
}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 15: CANCELACIÓN DE VIAJE (Liberación de recursos)
### ============================================================================

### Cancelar el segundo viaje
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/trips/{{tripId2}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}

### Verificar que el camión sigue disponible
GET {{baseUrl}}/fleet/trucks/{{truckId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Verificar que el conductor sigue disponible
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/{{driverId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 16: ESTADÍSTICAS FINALES
### ============================================================================

### Estadísticas de viajes
GET {{baseUrl}}/trips/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Estadísticas de fronteras
GET {{baseUrl}}/border-crossings/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Estadísticas de liquidaciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/settlements/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Estadísticas de facturas
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 17: INTENTO DE USAR RECURSOS OCUPADOS
### ============================================================================

### Crear un tercer viaje
# @name createTrip3
POST {{baseUrl}}/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "micDta": "MIC-AUTO-TEST-003",
  "departureDate": "2024-06-22T06:00:00Z",
  "billOfLadingId": "{{blId}}",
  "truckId": "{{truckId}}",
  "driverId": "{{driverId}}",
  "weight": 28.0,
  "ratePerTon": 150.00
}

@tripId3 = {{createTrip3.response.body.data.id}}

### Poner en tránsito
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/trips/{{tripId3}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "IN_TRANSIT"
}

### Intentar crear otro viaje con el mismo camión (debe fallar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "micDta": "MIC-AUTO-TEST-004",
  "departureDate": "2024-06-22T08:00:00Z",
  "billOfLadingId": "{{blId}}",
  "truckId": "{{truckId}}",
  "driverId": "{{driverId}}",
  "weight": 20.0,
  "ratePerTon": 150.00
}

### ============================================================================
### PRUEBA 18: LIMPIEZA - COMPLETAR VIAJE DE PRUEBA
### ============================================================================

### Entregar el tercer viaje
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/trips/{{tripId3}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "DELIVERED"
}

### ============================================================================
### RESUMEN DE ENDPOINTS PROBADOS
### ============================================================================
###
### AUTOMATIZACIONES PROBADAS:
### 1. ✅ SCHEDULED → IN_TRANSIT: Marca truck IN_TRANSIT, driver unavailable
### 2. ✅ IN_TRANSIT → AT_BORDER: Marca truck AT_BORDER, auto-crea BorderCrossing
### 3. ✅ AT_BORDER → IN_TRANSIT: Marca truck IN_TRANSIT (al salir de frontera)
### 4. ✅ * → DELIVERED: Libera todos los recursos
### 5. ✅ * → CANCELLED: Libera todos los recursos
### 6. ✅ Validación: No permite usar recursos ocupados
### 7. ✅ Validación: No permite liquidar viajes no entregados
###
### NUEVOS ENDPOINTS:
### - GET /border-crossings (con paginación y filtros)
### - GET /border-crossings/names
### - GET /settlements/calculate/:tripId
### - POST /invoices/calculate
###
### ============================================================================
